data.description: Multiple Offers Received! All offers will be viewed Friday evening and Final Offers Due no later the Sunday at 5pm!! This 5 bedroom 3.5 Bath home located on a Golf course in a highly desired area, has lots of potential. With a little TLC, you can make this house the home of your dreams! With a 3 car garage and wide drive way, there is plenty of space to park you and your family's vehicles. Great Investment opportunity for a someone who wants to remodel a home and use it as a rental or fix and flip!
